.TH "update_tx_opstats" 9 "update_tx_opstats" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
update_tx_opstats \- record stats by opcode
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" update_tx_opstats
.BI "(struct rvt_qp *qp "  ","
.BI "struct hfi1_pkt_state *ps "  ","
.BI "u32 plen "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "qp" 12
the qp
.IP "ps" 12
transmit packet state
.IP "plen" 12
the plen in dwords
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
This is a routine to record the tx opstats after a
packet has been presented to the egress mechanism.
